A family with acquired and inherited blue-yellow axis.
 The pedigree of a family with a blue-yellow axis in the Farnsworth 100-Hue is reported.
 The fact that a blue-yellow axis corresponds to an inherited defect in 6 subjects and to an acquired defect in 1 subject is discussed.
 Methodological conditions necessary for making the differential diagnosis between an inherited and an acquired blue-yellow defect are recalled.
